The paper discusses the use of deep learning in steganography and steganalysis, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper specifically focuses on the evaluation of different neural networks for steganalysis, which involves image processing and computer vision techniques (cs.CV). The use of deep learning also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses steganography by GAN, which involves multimedia processing (cs.MM).
